.SH NAME
arx-hook-uninstall - Uninstall the pre-commit hook


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBarx hook uninstall [path] [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Remove the pre-commit hook from the git repository.

.PP
Removes .git/hooks/pre-commit if it was previously installed.
If no hook is installed, prints a message and exits successfully.

.PP
If no path is provided, the current directory is used.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for uninstall


